name: WetMeWild
description: WetMeWild is the fantasy of being a Slavic water nymph, a mythical creature with special seductive powers, living in a river and small forest streams. Her creation, appearance, used artifacts, and performed gestures are a game of associations that refer to existing mythology. All her activities are involved in the protection and worshipping of water during environmental degradation, as well as in the concept of responsible communication in a time of developed technology, online presence, and domination of the corporate system.
